e 都潛在好 critical 嘅 security issue<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 搵易進攻嘅入口</strong><br />\n只要搵啲 software 一 search<br />\neg. Acunetix Vulnerability Scanner<br />\n<br />\n就會掃晒出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 攻城</strong><br />\n咁有啲立心不良嘅人就可以根據佢 scan 出嚟嘅 vulnerability 搵相應嘅黑客軟件進行攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 搶掠 + 俘虜敵軍</strong><br />\n咁如果嗰啲人入到去對方嘅 server，除咗可以偷 data，仲可以放 remote access trojan (RAT)，咁對方部 server 就會成為傀儡，可以控制對方部 server 攻擊其他目標（黑客版 TeamViewer）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：建議大家唔好學，犯法㗎，俾人告就無謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e34585e77b986c54fd5ecee8a977d87b54461a0","tid":2285513,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T01:52:59.000Z","msg":"搵中級黑客netsend拜師先"},{"pid":"a443e02c70417d323f349e7932248af5a5fe4757","tid":2285513,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"比錢我教你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95079347a5a34ae9279fa7dc299febf61c051523","tid":2285513,"uid":59832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89e45a12a305c0bc5828dea7f6c70ef4ca10181c","tid":2285513,"uid":55583,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"香港有個中級黑客<br />\n可以搵佢拜師"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"netsend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9040921435811b23a458f749fc11129af7e0e268","tid":2285513,"uid":349995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"印度口音"}]}